    en: "The Village of Spencerport's building permit functions are performed by the Town of Ogden under a shared-services arrangement. For building permits — including roofing — the Town of Ogden Building Department at [number being verified] is the permit office for properties inside village limits. The village employs a part-time Code Enforcement Officer for property maintenance and village-specific code compliance. Building permit applications, plan review, and construction inspections all go through Ogden. This is a different model from most Monroe County villages, which run their own building departments."
